				},
				"string" : "Scripts are files that contain[[SmaCC Transformation Toolkit rewrite rules]],[[SmaCC Transformation Toolkit methods]], [[SmaCC Transformation Toolkit properties]], or imports of other script files. When AST nodes are processed by the script, the rules are processed in order that they appear in the script. "
